{"tha-ap229:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap229:0.2":"Alambanadayakavagga ","tha-ap229:0.3":"Sovannavatamsakiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap229:1.1":"“Uyyanabhumim niyyanto, ","tha-ap229:1.2":"addasam lokanayakam; ","tha-ap229:1.3":"Vatamsakam gahetvana, ","tha-ap229:1.4":"sovannam sadhunimmitam. ","tha-ap229:2.1":"Sigham tato samaruyha, ","tha-ap229:2.2":"hatthikkhandhagato aham; ","tha-ap229:2.3":"Buddhassa abhiropesim, ","tha-ap229:2.4":"sikhino lokabandhuno. ","tha-ap229:3.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap229:3.2":"yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap229:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap229:3.4":"pupphapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap229:4.1":"Sattavise ito kappe, ","tha-ap229:4.2":"eko asim janadhipo; ","tha-ap229:4.3":"Mahapatapanamena, ","tha-ap229:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap229:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap229:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap229:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap229:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sovannavatamsakiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap229:7.1":"Sovannavatamsakiyattherassapadanam sattamam. "}